<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="373" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[491,1529,1754,2020]" pageId="3" pageNumber="373">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[531,662,1824,1848]" pageId="3" pageNumber="373">Description</emphasis>
— Male: Idiosoma dorsally 721 long and 583 wide, ventrally 713 long. Dorsal shield complete, 300 long and 340 wide. Posterior to dorsal shield three irregularly shaped areas with a finer porosity.
</paragraph>
